onnection Establishment and termination.


Open a new terminal and start ­­TCP server using nc(netcad) command with l,k (keep alive)option
nc -lk 12345



Open another terminal and start TCP client using telnet to establish TCP connection with TCP server of step 1.
telnet 127.0.0.1 12345

In original terminal Perform tcpdump with specify local interface and port 12345
sudo tcpdump -i lo -nnn port 12345.
